<% 
    @title = "Antivoid Shop - Toko Online Premium & Modern"
    @description = "Selamat datang di Antivoid Shop. Temukan koleksi produk gaya hidup premium dengan desain modern Glassmorphism."
%>
<div class="relative overflow-hidden pt-12 pb-20 px-6">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full glass bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 text-sm font-bold mb-6 border border-indigo-100 uppercase tracking-widest">Koleksi Baru 2026</span>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-[1.1] mb-8">
                Upgrade Gaya Hidup <br/>
                <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600">Masa Depan Anda</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 mb-10 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
                Temukan koleksi produk pilihan berkualitas tinggi dengan desain modern dan performa terbaik di Antivoid Shop.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                <a href="/shop" class="group bg-indigo-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg shadow-xl shadow-indigo-200 hover:bg-indigo-700 hover:shadow-indigo-300 transition flex items-center gap-2">
                    Belanja Sekarang <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="/categories" class="glass px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/80 transition text-slate-700 flex items-center gap-2">
                    Telusuri Kategori
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-8 grayscale opacity-50">
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a9/Amazon_logo.svg" alt="Brand" class="h-6">
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2f/Google_2015_logo.svg" alt="Brand" class="h-6">
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/ba/Stripe_Logo%2C_revised_2016.svg" alt="Brand" class="h-8">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative animate__animated animate__fadeInRight">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-indigo-400 blur-[120px] opacity-20 rounded-full translate-x-10 translate-y-10"></div>
            <div class="glass p-4 rounded-[40px] shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden border border-white/60">
                <img class="rounded-[30px] w-full aspect-square md:aspect-auto md:h-[500px] object-cover" 
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" 
                    alt="Featured Product">
                <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 glass p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl max-w-xs animate__animated animate__fadeInUp animate__delay-1s border border-white/50">
                    <p class="text-indigo-600 font-bold text-sm mb-1 uppercase tracking-tight">Edisi Terbatas</p>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">UltraBoost X v2.0</h3>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900"><%= ViewHelper.format_rupiah(189.99) %></span>
                        <a href="/shop" class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-600 transition">
                            <i data-lucide="plus" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Featured Products Grid -->
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-12">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Produk Unggulan</h2>
            <div class="h-1.5 w-20 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        <a href="/shop" class="text-indigo-600 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-2 transition-all">
            Lihat Semua <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <% Product.all.take(4).each do |product| %>
            <div class="group glass rounded-3xl p-4 hover-lift border border-white/40 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-indigo-100">
                <div class="relative aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-6 bg-slate-100">
                    <img src="<%= product.image_url || 'https://via.placeholder.com/400' %>" 
                        alt="<%= product.name %>" 
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-700 group-hover:scale-110">
                    <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 animate-pulse">
                        <span class="glass-dark text-white text-[10px] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest bg-indigo-600/50">Populer</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="px-2">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 line-clamp-1 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition"><%= product.name %></h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-indigo-600"><%= ViewHelper.format_rupiah(product.price) %></p>
                        <a href="/product?id=<%= product.id %>" class="bg-white border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 p-2 rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-600 hover:text-white hover:border-indigo-600 transition shadow-sm">
                            <i data-lucide="eye" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        <% end %>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Benefits Section -->
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 mb-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="glass p-8 rounded-[32px] border border-white/60">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <i data-lucide="truck" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Pengiriman Cepat</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500">Nikmati layanan pengiriman prioritas yang menjangkau seluruh wilayah dalam waktu singkat.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass p-8 rounded-[32px] border border-white/60">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Garansi Aman</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500">Setiap produk kami dijamin keasliannya dan dilindungi garansi resmi untuk keamanan Anda.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass p-8 rounded-[32px] border border-white/60">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <i data-lucide="headset" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Layanan 24/7</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500">Tim bantuan kami siap melayani pertanyaan Anda kapan saja melalui live chat dan email.</p>
    </div>
</div>
